{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-0-10-12-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-document-tsx","path":"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"AntV","githubUrl":"https://github.com/antvis","docs":[{"slug":"specification/principles","title":{"zh":"设计原则","en":"Design Principles"},"order":0},{"slug":"specification/components","title":{"zh":"图表组件设计指引","en":"Design for Components of Charts"},"order":1}]},"pathPrefix":""},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>标题是对图表的主题进行阐述的一段话。<br />注释是表明数据来源，让图表看起来来源清晰、可靠。</p>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>让阅读者直观地阅读当前图表的主题，了解当前内容的来源。</p>\n<h2 id=\"内容和位置\"><a href=\"#%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE\" aria-label=\"内容和位置 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>内容和位置</h2>\n<p><strong>标题内容：</strong>言简意赅，尽量避免被截断；<br /><strong>标题位置：</strong>正、副标题一般放置于卡片左上角，标题宽度不超过卡片宽度。<br /><strong>注释内容：</strong>引用内容、数据来源等，保证正确性；<br /><strong>注释位置：</strong>一般放置于卡片左下角</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1、标题过长怎么办？\"><a href=\"#1%E3%80%81%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E8%BF%87%E9%95%BF%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"1、标题过长怎么办？ permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1、标题过长怎么办？</h3>\n<p>尽量精简标题内容，当标题过长且超过了卡片宽度时，请省略标题中间的文字，保住首尾，如“我是...标题”。<br />若副标题过长时，最多折 2 行，高度不超过卡片的 30%。</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes/#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\">定义</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes/#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">何时使用</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes/#%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE\">内容和位置</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes/#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\">常见问题</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes/#1%E3%80%81%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E8%BF%87%E9%95%BF%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%EF%BC%9F\">1、标题过长怎么办？</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes","readingTime":{"text":"1 min read","time":6900}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Title and Notes"},"parent":{"relativePath":"specification/components/titlenotes.en.md"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计原则","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Principles","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Visual","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"视觉","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/interact"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Interact","order":2}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/interact"},"frontmatter":{"title":"交互","order":2}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Title and Notes","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/titlenotes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"标题与注释","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/mobile"},"frontmatter":{"title":"移动","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/mobile"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mobile","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Axis","order":4}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"轴","order":4}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图例","order":5}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Legend","order":5}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Label","order":6}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"标签","order":6}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"提示信息","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图形设计指引","order":8}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/resources"},"frontmatter":{"title":"资源下载","order":10}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/resources"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Resource Download","order":10}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/reference"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Classical Literature","order":11}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/reference"},"frontmatter":{"title":"经典文献","order":11}}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"prev":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Label","order":6},"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>在图表中，标签是对当前的一组数据进行的内容标注。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"元素\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素</h2>\n<p>包括数据点、拉线、文本数值等元素，根据不同的图表类型选择使用。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*iufiSLxK90oAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<h2 id=\"显示策略\"><a href=\"#%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\" aria-label=\"显示策略 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>显示策略</h2>\n<p>通常标签显示在图形外，但在「堆叠类」图表中，标签会显示在图形内。如下图：<br /><img src='' width=377/><br />标签的文本和图形经常需要交叠展示，所以可读性需要足够良好，所以通过对 HS 值的判断，决定文字的颜色。这样对比度就在可控范围内，不会出现可读性的问题。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*ch10Q6ixqCIAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=250/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"问题-1：图表标签重叠时怎么办？\"><a href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-1%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%BE%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%A0%E6%97%B6%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"问题 1：图表标签重叠时怎么办？ permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>问题 1：图表标签重叠时怎么办？</h3>\n<p>标签重叠时，g2plot 的默认方案为动态计算的抽样显示，在标签重叠时，自动隐藏其中一个，同时当 Hover 图表时，显示被隐藏的对应的数据。这样保证了图表的清晰度，也保证了信息的完整性。<br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*NoZ0Q7S8mzkAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=259/></p>\n<h3 id=\"问题-2：我可以自定义标签吗？\"><a href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-2%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%97%EF%BC%9F\" aria-label=\"问题 2：我可以自定义标签吗？ permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>问题 2：我可以自定义标签吗？</h3>\n<p>可以，通过配置项你可以修改标签的样式，包括点的形状、文字大小等，但我们还是建议您使用默认方案。</p>"}},"next":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7},"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>提示信息 Tooltip，指当鼠标悬停在图表上或者手指点按移动设备的某个数据点时，<strong>以交互提示</strong>信息的形式展示该点的数据，比如该点的值，数据单位等。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>当你希望数据可视化作品对用户的操作有所反馈时，提示信息 Tooltip 就可以发挥作用。<br />例如：当用户悬停一个数据点时，如果仅数据点样式发生变化而没有其他任何提示，这看起来就像一个 Bug，建议同步显示提示信息 Tooltip 帮助用户深入了解数据点的详情。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"元素\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\" aria-label=\"元素 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>元素</h2>\n<p>Tooltip 的基本元素包括：视觉标记图形，文本标签，数值标记等。 <br />Tooltip 的可选元素：所在的 UI 容器还可以和其他 UI 组件配合使用，完成过滤，下钻等自助分析功能。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/basement_prod/0677c002-9804-4d12-9d3f-744ec5d3c763.svg' width=750/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"类型\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h2>\n<p>提示信息 Tooltip 按不同的图表类型，常见有如下四种：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>跟随显示的浮层提示</th>\n<th>与图例组合显示的提示</th>\n<th>与轴组合显示的提示</th>\n<th>图形上显示的提示</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>悬浮</td>\n<td>固定位置</td>\n<td>固定在轴上</td>\n<td>固定在图形上</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*jWBiQa_9An0AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=243/></td>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*863pQ7Uw3y8AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></td>\n<td>[<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*DB8JTaxMB3sAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=292/></td>\n<td><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*qjY2Sp_5kCwAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=350/></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"跟随显示的浮层提示\"><a href=\"#%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%AE%E5%B1%82%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"跟随显示的浮层提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>跟随显示的浮层提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*I-40QY9l0qsAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>PC 端<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>悬浮即触发显示，跟随鼠标移动<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>全部图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"与图例组合显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%BE%E4%BE%8B%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"与图例组合显示的提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>与图例组合显示的提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*YzfWTYhikzYAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>常用于移动端，PC 端也适用<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>图表上方<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>全部图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"与轴组合显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8E%E8%BD%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"与轴组合显示的提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>与轴组合显示的提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*iiTwS5EqJ94AAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>常用于 PC 端，移动端也可使用<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>轴上，覆盖轴标签<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>散点图、气泡图等迪卡尔坐标系图表</p>\n<h3 id=\"图形上显示的提示\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"图形上显示的提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>图形上显示的提示</h3>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*q7hcQYsi6NsAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<p><strong>适合设备：</strong>PC 端、移动端均可<br /><strong>出现位置：</strong>图形上<br /><strong>适合图表类型：</strong>环图</p>"}}}}}